data.description: This elegant 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom single-family oasis exudes the laid-back charm of island living. Situated on a serene corner lot, this home has undergone a complete renovation and is just a stone's throw away from everything that you need! Being sold with brand new furnishings and has a 30 Y assume 5.625% annual percentage rate VA loan.As you step onto the property, you'll be enveloped in a cocoon of privacy, thanks to the arched cement walls that encircle the entire home. These walls create a tranquil sanctuary on this large, 6,000 SF lot, shielding the private pool area, where a graceful coral waterfall adds to the soothing ambiance. This oasis is move-in ready, with a plethora of brand-new improvements designed to enhance your island experience. The new HVAC system (2022) ensures year-round comfort, while the resurfaced pool, complete with luxurious marble decking and a custom bar, invites you to indulge in relaxation and entertainment. The modern bathrooms, new washer and dryer (2022), storage galore and upscale vinyl plank flooring all contribute to the home's fresh, coastal appeal.The kitchen is updated with all stainless-steel appliances (2022) including a gas range. With its wood cabinetry, gleaming quartz countertops, and an extended tile backsplash, this kitchen is ready for your culinary expertise. It's a space where you can prepare scrumptious meals while relishing the island breeze.Additionally, there's a private entrance to the master bedroom that can be used for an in-law suite, providing flexibility and convenience for your guests. This room can be locked off from the main living area and has a huge walk in closet! There is space for 2 private gated parking spots within the walls and off-street parking for 3-4 cars. Home is being sold fully furnished.  Move in ready!Embrace the Key West lifestyle and make this oasis your own today!
